Class FacebookObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.social.facebook.api.FacebookObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Account, Achievement, AchievementType, Album, Comment, CoverPhoto, Device, EducationExperience, Engagement, Event, EventInvitee, Experience, Group, GroupMembership, Invitation, Location, MailingAddress, MessageTag, Page, PaymentPricePoint, PaymentPricePoints, Photo, Place, Post, ProfilePictureSource, Reference, SecuritySettings, SecuritySettings.SecureBrowsing, Tag, User, UserIdForApp, UserInvitableFriend, UserTaggableFriend, Video, VideoUploadLimits, VoipInfo, WorkEntry

    public abstract class FacebookObject
extends Object
    Base class for all Facebook types. Offers an extraData property for carrying any data in response from Facebook that won't be otherwise mapped to any properties of the subclass.
